Anand Verma | Climate Leader | AI | Investor | YPO Anand is the Founder and CEO of Expect AI. A London based Climate AI company, serving the world, committed to helping companies decarbonise, profitably with the power of data and AI. Prior to his recent venture, Anand was the Founder and CEO of Brilliant Basics, an award winning Global Design and Innovation company headquartered in London with studios all over the globe. Successfully exited to technology conglomerate Infosys in 2017 to accelerate their Design and Innovation business  globally. Anand led Infosys’ digital capabilities of £700m+. Deeply involved with leading the academia <> industry partnerships to create impactful collaboration at scale. Anand is a digital, AI and sustainability visionary, innovator and successful entrepreneur who has a deep understanding of planet, people and technology needs. Holding over 27 years’ of professional experience in management consulting, digital and impactful businesses. He is passionate about creating positive change by humanising technology. Previously, Anand was one of the youngest Presidents and CEO's at Interpublic Group (IPG) leading Mediabrands Ventures leading their digital and ventures (M&A) arm. Previous to this, Anand held senior leadership roles at Publicis Sapient. In 2019, Anand made a personal and professional commitment to dedicate his life to fighting the climate change with the power of design, data and AI solutions. Additionally, Anand is also the chairman of an early stage AI company Reimagine AI as well as advises various startups and scale-ups in the impact space. In 2021, he received honorary Doctorate in Computer Science from his alma mater for his services to design and technology. He has also received his Corporate Strategy and M&A certification from INSEAD. He is based in London with his lovely wife and two beautiful children.
